title: CONSIDER CALLING THIS APT "HOME"; AVAIL 8/15
posting_body: ["Northeast's neighborhood can be divided into two main sections: the Arts district and the Riverfront district.", 'You can access parts of these sections or all of it from this great apartment conveniently located near:', '--Multiple restaurants, featuring a variety of cuisines', '--Bike trails', '--Parks', '--Shopping', '--Entertainment', 'Location and Transportation:', '--Access to major highways and even great street by which to go to Minneapolis, St Paul and/or our Suburban cities', '--Access to several bus lines to travel on to travel the Twin Cities and our Suburban cities', '--Downtown Minneapolis, Uptown Minneapolis, St. Paul', 'Features and Facts:', '--Great upper-level apartment.', 'Two good-sized Bedrooms, both with Closet space, a Bathroom with both Tub and Shower.', '--Newly refurbished Hardwood Floors throughout the apartment', '--Appliances: Range, Microwave, Refrigerator, Dishwasher, a Washer and a Dryer', '--Common areas between the upper and lower apartments include the front Porch and a fenced-in front, side, and back Yard, with space for a Garden', '--Off-street Parking', '--Owner pays for Water, Trash, and Sewage', '--Tenant(s) pay for the utilities (gas and electric)', "--Tenant(s) will need to carry renter's insurance", '--This is a Non-smoking building', '--No Pets, please', '--24-month Rental Agreement', '--Security Deposit: $1625', 'Available for move in on August 15.', 'Email us soon to set an appointment!']
